com.devtence.will.dev.endpoints.commons

Class FileAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.devtence.will.dev.endpoints.commons.FileAPI

  • public class FileAPI
extends java.lang.Object
    Google Endpoint Class that implements the API methods to create resumable upload sessions to the Google Cloud Datastore, it can create sessions for single files or multiple files.

    All the methods on this class are secured by the default Authenticator. Note: to create resumable sessions it's necessary to create and add a google certification file with a valid service account, otherwise it will not be able to create the session.

    Since:
    2016-06-06
    Author:
    plessmann
    See Also:
